pl.edu.mimuw.changeanalyzer.models.standard

Class StandardDataSetBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • pl.edu.mimuw.changeanalyzer.models.DataSetBuilder
      • pl.edu.mimuw.changeanalyzer.models.ChunkDataSetBuilder
        • pl.edu.mimuw.changeanalyzer.models.standard.StandardDataSetBuilder

  • public class StandardDataSetBuilder
extends ChunkDataSetBuilder
    This data set builder class uses commit group as model. Each produced instance represents a group of subsequent commits starting with a commit directly succeeding a bug-fix. Groups contain from one commit up to a whole chunk.
    Author:
    Adam Wierzbicki
